In {{ill|1890|ja|1890年|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1890|qq=}} ({{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 23 year), it was moved to {{ill|Furuishiba|ja|古石場|lt=Fukagawa Furuishibacho|lt_ja=深川古石場町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Furuishiba|qq=}}. Both the {{ill|Great Kantō earthquake|ja|関東大震災|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Great Kantō earthquake|qq=}} and the {{ill|Tokyo air raid|ja|東京大空襲|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokyo air raid|qq=}} burned the structures, and after the war, the sacred spirit was transferred to the Asahi Shrine of the main shrine in {{ill|Sanuki Province|ja|讃岐国|lt=Sanuki|lt_ja=讃岐|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sanuki Province|qq=}}.

In {{ill|1956|ja|1956年|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1956|qq=}} ({{ill|Shōwa era|ja|昭和|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōwa era|qq=}} 31 year), from Matsudaira Yoriaki (Count) of the former {{ill|Takamatsu Domain|ja|高松藩|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takamatsu Domain|qq=}}, belonging to the {{ill|Takamatsu Matsudaira Family|ja|高松松平家|lt=Tatsudaira family|lt_ja=松平家|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takamatsu Matsudaira Family|qq=}}, a donation of the land of the former {{ill|Kamiyashiki|ja|上屋敷|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamiyashiki|qq=}} of the Sanuki Takamatsu Domain was received. This land, previously used for establishing the {{ill|Suidobashi (Kandagawa)|ja|水道橋 (神田川)|lt=Suidobashi|lt_ja=水道橋|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suidobashi (Kandagawa)|qq=}} {{ill|Kotohira shrines|lt=Kotohira shrines|lt=Konpira Shrine|ja|金刀比羅神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konpira Shrine|qq=}}, founded in {{ill|1793|ja|1793rd year|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1793|qq=}} ({{ill|Kansei era|ja|寛政|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei era|qq=}} 5 year), enabled the two shrines to be enshrined together, and the relocation and restoration were completed in {{ill|1964|ja|1964年|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1964|qq=}} ({{ill|Shōwa era|ja|昭和|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōwa era|qq=}} 39 year).

